  "special": {
    "title": "Did I fire six shots, or only five? Three? Seven. Whatever.",
    "description": "Consumes 3 ammo per shot, or more with Double Penetrating. Fires one projectile that rapidly splits into a horizontal spread of explosive shots. The center splash gets full grenade-damage scaling, while the spawned projectiles use a smaller splash scale."
  },
  "notes": "Split distance scales with accuracy, so higher accuracy delays the spread. Double Penetrating versions fire two parallel bursts and use 6 ammo per trigger pull. The spawned projectiles are not listed on the item card, and each can receive full amp damage. Projectile speed boosts push the split farther out, hurting point-blank performance but improving longer-range consistency.",
